<p><a name="Novels" id="Novels"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Martin_Amis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: Novels">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Novels</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Rachel_Papers_(novel)" title="The Rachel Papers (novel)">The Rachel Papers</a></i> (1973), <a href="/wiki/The_Rachel_Papers" title="The Rachel Papers">filmed</a> in 1989</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Dead_Babies_(novel)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Dead Babies (novel) (page does not exist)">Dead Babies</a></i> (1975), filmed in 2000</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Success_(novel)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Success (novel) (page does not exist)">Success</a></i> (1978)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Other_People" title="Other People">Other People</a></i> (1981)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Money_(novel)" title="Money (novel)">Money</a></i> (1984)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/London_Fields_(novel)" title="London Fields (novel)">London Fields</a></i> (1989)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Time%27s_Arrow_(novel)" title="Time's Arrow (novel)">Time's Arrow: Or the Nature of the Offence</a></i> (1991)</li>
